The so-called university spirit refers to a series of educational concepts and value pursuits accumulated by a university in the process of development for a long time, which is the soul of the university.
From ancient times to the present, the spirit of the university has been crucial to the political, economic, cultural, scientific and technological, social development, and even the progress of a nation.
Since the birth of the world's first university in the modern sense, the university has shouldered a unique mission different from other social organizations, for China's universities, arising in the autumn of national crisis, its spirit is deeply affected by traditional culture and changes of the times, advocating the value concept of "Mingde Ji Shi, Xiu Qi Zhi Ping" and the patriotic responsibility of "rejuvenating the country with learning".
At present, the trend of informatization and internationalization of higher education is becoming increasingly obvious, the global competition in education, science and technology, and talent competition is intensifying, and the structural reform of higher education as an important "supply side" is facing unprecedented opportunities and challenges.
In particular, the proposal of the "Overall Plan for Comprehensively Promoting the Construction of World-Class Universities and First-class Disciplines" not only demonstrates China's confidence and determination to move from a big country in higher education to a strong country in higher education, but also puts forward higher and newer requirements for the development of universities.
How to strive to become one of the world's most popular in a relatively short period of time, accelerate the construction of a number of world-class universities and a number of world-class disciplines on the basis of still a certain gap, and achieve "overtaking in curves"?
In addition to firm goal confidence, path confidence, and ability confidence, colleges and universities should also give full play to three advantages: First, the advantage of being a latecomer, through the continuous introduction of overseas outstanding academic talents, learning from the advanced experience of world-class universities, to achieve a significant improvement in academic level and school quality; The second is cultural advantages, inheriting the wisdom connotation accumulated by Chinese civilization in the past 5,000 years, and carrying forward and developing excellent traditional culture, so as to gather strength, shape brands, and enhance image; The third is institutional advantages, giving full play to the institutional superiority of socialist countries, strengthening goal-driven, pooling consensus and synergy, optimizing resource allocation, and providing a sustainable and solid guarantee for schools to accelerate catch-up and surpass the world's advanced level.
In particular, it is necessary to realize that the construction of a world-class university cannot be a thousand schools, and each school must show its personality and characteristics while giving full play to its advantages.
The characteristics of running a school should not only have common Chinese characteristics, but also reflect their unique goal positioning, school-running traditions and resource endowments.
As far as Zhejiang University is concerned, we pay attention to highlighting three characteristics in running the school: First, highlight the characteristics of innovative and entrepreneurial talent training, build an integrated education environment that integrates science and education and combines school and enterprise, and forms a whole-chain entrepreneurial education ecosystem; The second is to highlight the characteristics of interdisciplinary convergence, promote the optimization and adjustment of the discipline system, create an institutional environment for interdisciplinary disciplines, and actively cultivate cross-emerging disciplines and landmark cross-cutting achievements; The third is to highlight the characteristics of the school-running system and social services, carry out in-depth international exchanges and cooperation, and accelerate the formation of a pan-Zhejiang university-university-research cooperation system.
In this process, it is particularly important to always adhere to the spirit of the university and let the spirit of the university resonate with the spirit of the times.
For Zhejiang University, the school motto of "Seeking Truth and Innovation", the common values of "Diligence, Moral Cultivation, Discernment and Solidity" and "Haina River, Qizhen Houde, Pioneering People, and Building Our Country" together constitute the latest expression system of the spirit of Zhejiang University.
This is an important guarantee for the school to adhere to the correct direction of running the school, continuously accumulate cultural height, and gather spiritual strength, which is rich in connotation and far-reaching significance.
Among them, "Haina River" emphasizes the spirit of openness and inclusiveness, embodies the mind of "the world's talents are used by me", and is expressed as the high-quality concept of learning from the world's famous schools; "Qi Zhen HouDe" emphasizes the spirit of seeking truth and being kind, which refers to the fact that while pursuing the truth, universities should also receive the cultivation of virtue and the improvement of personality; "Pioneering the people" embodies the spirit of reform and innovation, which not only includes the innovation of knowledge, the innovation of scientific research, but also the reform and development, the revolution of the old and the new; "Building Our Nation" emphasizes the spirit of patriotic dedication and talks about the fact that universities should always share the glory and disgrace of the fate of the nation.
This series of spiritual concepts and value pursuits is the soul of Zhejiang University's 120 years of education.
"The wise hear in silence, and the wise see in the invisible."
Chinese colleges and universities should further base themselves on the overall situation of the cause of socialism with Chinese characteristics, profoundly grasp the orientation of the times and the historical mission shouldered by the cause of higher education, and accelerate the construction of a world-class university.
At the same time, we should adhere to humanistic care and independence and freedom, so that the spirit of the university, the spirit of the times and the spirit of the nation can stir each other, so as to provide an inexhaustible driving force for the realization of national prosperity and national rejuvenation, and the realization of the common ideals of mankind.
