Educational Thinking: How College Examinations Can Make "Academic Bullies" and "Scum of Learning" Get Their Own Places - Xinhua Net
Three students of Lanzhou Jiaotong University wrote a letter to the school leaders, reflecting their confusion about the university examination, and proposed to improve the difficulty of the examination, change the type of examination questions, and let the examination truly reflect the actual level of students.
Indeed, college exams have long been a "hot topic."
On university campuses, students come from all over the world, with varying levels of ability, coupled with varying levels of learning.
For the assessment of groups with such diverse characteristics, it is inevitable that there will be different feelings.
Of course, if the test question type is single, the repetition rate is high, and the questions are too simple, it will inevitably cause another completely different feeling.
Students who do not use work may be able to pass the pre-exam concentrated assault, and if they think of other methods, it is possible to achieve the effect of doubling the results with half the effort.
In this way, there will be "scum" who can pass the pass without investing in it, and even get a high score; "Xueba" usually never falls behind, the homework and notes are good, and the exam is not much higher than the "strange status quo".
In this way, the students of Lanzhou Jiaotong University reflect that the problems existing in the university examination are not without reason, and it is believed that this situation is not only the existence of Lanzhou Jiaotong University.
In this sense, I would like to praise these 3 students who wrote straight letters.
In fact, people who have gone to college know very well that it is not uncommon to surprisely prepare for the exam, think of various ways to "take" the exam questions from the teacher, strive to draw the scope of the exam, and seek "key counseling" before the exam, and even the situation of carrying a small copy in the exam and asking the teacher to raise his noble hand after the exam is not a strange thing.
In the author's view, as a teaching quality evaluation orientation, the measure of whether a university examination is passed or not lies in the teacher's comprehensive grasp of teaching and learning, and the scientific proposition on this basis.
Entering the undergraduate stage, the major begins to subdivide, and many professional courses are based on basic knowledge.
Undoubtedly, whether or not to fully grasp the basic knowledge points of a discipline is the content of the university examination.
The undergraduate knowledge is basically the basic theory and basic common sense of the discipline, from the knowledge point, the space for change is not large, basically fixed.
As some teachers have said, "The basic knowledge of university mathematics 20 years ago is still being learned, and it is still the focus." ”
However, the knowledge points are basically unchanged, which does not mean that the test question type is single and the test questions are repeated.
In many universities, the examination will generally form a question group, and then the senior teachers of the subject will coordinate the composition of the examination paper, and the examination paper will also be participated by all the teachers who undertake the subject, so that the duplication of the examination questions can be overcome to a certain extent.
However, to draw up a set of test questions that meet the actual teaching and learning, the topics are normally distributed according to the overall situation of students' learning, and it is also necessary to comprehensively grasp the teaching situation and comprehensively analyze the degree of students' learning, so that the examination propositions have a dynamic grasp of the difficulty and question type, which can highlight the basic knowledge examination, but also take into account the ability examination, and at the same time innovate the design of the question type.
Examinations are the baton of university education, what kind of examinations, students will have a corresponding preparation plan, in the long run, will affect the effectiveness of university education.
For the students' letter of recommendation, Lanzhou Jiaotong University attaches great importance to it and has deployed a rectification plan throughout the school.
All teaching units are required to organize teachers to carry out seminars and self-examinations of course completion examinations, formulate examination paper propositions and related systems, and at the same time strengthen the supervision and inspection of examination paper propositions and audit links, refine performance evaluation, and strengthen the comprehensive assessment of all aspects of course teaching.
From the mechanism to solve the problem of single type of test questions, repeated questions and other issues is the university examination need to face the topic, of course, the need to introduce the corresponding system, but the kung fu is expensive in daily life, the teacher needs to fully grasp the teaching situation, not only to eat through the teaching content, but also to eat through the student's learning situation, the two ends of the thorough, teaching and learning will be better docked, the formation of benign interaction, the examination will be more realistic, so that the "learning bully" and "scum" each have their place.
